Kykyaqil xnaq´tzanjtz n-chi kub´ we´ extzen n-chi ky-xo´n ky-tx´otx´ toj kya´j, noq o´kx Draco, a n-chi tzaj t-xo´n t-xu´k twitz mes.



Seamus: Neville! {N-chi tzaj tq´o´n tq´ob´.}



Kykyaqil n-chi ky-xupin ky-wi´x extzen n-chi ky-xo´n kyib´, n-chi tzalaj ex n-chi tze´n.



